---
title: "'Pensativo' ('Thinkable', not yet translated into English)"
format: "book"
category: "s"
yearReleased: "1885"
author: "Juan Serrano y Oteyza"
---
The author was a prominent anarchist in 19th century Spain. 'Pensativo' is a utopian novella, positing a possible Proudhonian mutualist society. Referenced in Nettlau's _Esbozo_ and the 2014 _Bottled Wasp Pocket Diary_.
